WEBVTT

00:03:58.440 --> 00:04:00.536
Naučile se bomo brati in pisati

00:04:00.560 --> 00:04:02.576
in ponovno vložile prošnjo, pa kaj?"

00:04:02.600 --> 00:04:08.000
(Aplavz)

00:04:09.600 --> 00:04:12.056
Začele smo s poukom branja in pisanja.

00:04:12.080 --> 00:04:14.616
Ženske so vsak dan prihajale.

00:04:14.640 --> 00:04:18.375
Tako odločene so bile,
da so po tem, ko so cel dan delale,

00:04:18.399 --> 00:04:21.856
prišle k pouku
in se učile brati in pisati.

00:04:21.880 --> 00:04:23.256
Po petih mesecih

00:04:23.280 --> 00:04:24.816
smo ponovno zaprosile,

00:04:24.840 --> 00:04:27.856
a tokrat nisem šla sama.

00:04:27.880 --> 00:04:31.240
Petnajst žensk me je pospremilo
v Reserve Bank of India.